The '''Knights''' are an {{2|Elites|Elite}} encounter found in {{2|Glory}}, featuring three knights fighting together.

== Flail Knight ==
{{Enemy Infobox|Flail Knight|2}}
=== Pattern ===
{{Intents|Flail Knight|2}}
Opens with {{Int|Flail Knight|Ram||2}}, then randomly uses {{Int|Flail Knight|Breaker||2}}, {{Int|Flail Knight|Flail||2}}, or {{Int|Flail Knight|Ram||2}} each turn. {{Int|Flail Knight|Breaker||2}} cannot be used two turns in a row. 

{{Clear}}

== Spectral Knight ==
{{Enemy Infobox|Spectral Knight|2}}{{Power Infobox|Hex|2}}
=== Pattern ===
{{Intents|Spectral Knight|2}}
Opens with {{Int|Spectral Knight|Hex||2}}. After that, alternates between {{Int|Spectral Knight|Soul Slash||2}} and {{Int|Spectral Knight|Soul Flame||2}}.

{{Clear}}

== Magi Knight ==
{{Enemy Infobox|Magi Knight|2}}{{Power Infobox|Dampen|2}}
=== Pattern ===
{{Intents|Magi Knight|2}}
Starts with {{Int|Magi Knight|Power Shield||2}}, followed by {{Int|Magi Knight|Dampen||2}}.
Then repeatedly uses {{Int|Magi Knight|Ram||2}}, {{Int|Magi Knight|Prep||2}}, and {{Int|Magi Knight|Magic Bomb||2}} in that order.


{{Clear}}

